Our character sprites are either directly taken or modified versions
of sprites from the game "Last Guardian" by Philipp Lenssen
(http://blogoscoped.com/archive/2006-08-08-n51.html). Thanks for
making them freely available under a creative common license
(http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/2.5/).

Most of our level tile graphics, many items like computer terminals,
the level exit, etc. are taken from or modified versions of sprites
from GfxLib
(http://www.spicypixel.net/2008/01/10/gfxlib-fuzed-a-free-developer-graphic-library/). These
files were made available under CPL 1.0 which states the following:

