The snowball graphic was modified from the Rock sprite at http://lunar.lostgarden.com/PlanetCute%20PNG.zip; thanks to Danc at http://www.lostgarden.com/2007/05/dancs-miraculously-flexible-game.html.

The fireball graphic was modified from the Exhaust3 sprite at http://lunar.lostgarden.com/files/Sinistar.zip; thanks to Danc at http://www.lostgarden.com/2005/03/download-complete-set-of-sweet-8-bit.html.

The explosion graphic was modified from the Explode3 sprite at http://lunar.lostgarden.com/files/Sinistar.zip; thanks to Danc at http://www.lostgarden.com/2005/03/download-complete-set-of-sweet-8-bit.html.